OL,6,FAndrea Scott spoke to ITV News
OL,7,FMeridian's Kara Digby about the ordeal.
OL,9,FWarning: this story contains details
OL,10,Fwhich some people may find distressing.
OL,12,FThe daughter of an 88-year-old
OL,13,FSouthampton woman, who had the entire
OL,14,Ftop of a toe chewed off by a rat, has
OL,15,Fdescribed her horror.
