OL,4,Coff by rat
OL,6,FAndrea Scott said: "You're in
OL,7,Fdisbelief, you're like, that can't
OL,8,Fhave happened, that surely can't have.
OL,9,FBut I knew when I saw the sock because
OL,10,Fnothing else would explain that sock
OL,11,Fand that amount of damage to her toe."
OL,13,FHer mum, Joan, lives in a council-
OL,14,Fowned house. She's bed-bound and has
OL,15,Fno feeling in her legs.
OL,17,FIn April, Andrea had contacted
OL,18,FSouthampton City Council for help
OL,19,Fafter seeing a rat run across the
OL,20,Ffloor.
