OL,6,FShe was told it would cost her mum
OL,7,Fnearly #300 for pest control to come
OL,8,Fand it would more than take two weeks.
OL,10,FSo she decided to lay traps and rat
OL,11,Fpoison herself, hoping it would
OL,12,Fprotect her mum.
OL,14,FThen, on May 20th, Scott received a
OL,15,Fshocking call from her mother's carers.
OL,17,F"When I came in, I saw the carers were
OL,18,Fin distress, upset. I came over to Mum
OL,19,Fand I just saw the toe and the top of
OL,20,Fit was gone and the blood, there was
OL,21,Fblood everywhere.
