OL,6,F"The top of the sock was gnawed off
OL,7,Fand her toe, the whole top half was
OL,8,Fmissing.
OL,10,F"I can't explain the shock.
OL,12,F"She at this point still couldn't feel
OL,13,Fanything, that's my only saving grace
OL,14,Fat this stage is she did not feel that
OL,15,Fhappen."
