OL,6,FAndrea said she's disappointed with
OL,7,FSouthampton City Council's lack of
OL,8,Fcare: "If she's got a broken window
OL,9,Fthe council come and fix it or if
OL,10,Fshe's got a leaky tap they would come
OL,11,Fand fix it, so why is it different
OL,12,Fbecause it's rats that they wont come
OL,13,Funless she pays?
OL,15,F"They've got a duty of care as her
OL,16,Flandlord. If a private tenant rented
OL,17,Fsomewhere their landlord would have to
OL,18,Fsort it.
OL,20,F"That's my thing that I'm so angry
OL,21,Fabout they just didn't seem to care."
