OL,6,FAndrea says the council arranged to
OL,7,Fsee the property yesterday (Thursday
OL,8,F29th) but no one showed up and she
OL,9,Fhasn't heard from them since.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Southampton City
OL,12,FCouncil said: "We understand how
OL,13,Fdistressing it can be to experience a
OL,14,Fpest issue, and we take all reports
OL,15,Fseriously.
