OL,6,F"We encourage residents to let us know
OL,7,Fabout any sightings through our
OL,8,Fwebsite, or customer service telephone
OL,9,Fnumber, so our team can promptly
OL,10,Fassess the situation and work together
OL,11,Fto find a solution.
OL,13,F"In response to a report made
OL,14,Fyesterday, Tuesday 27 May, which
OL,15,Fraised the issues of a rat infestation
OL,16,Fand potentially unsafe electrics, the
OL,17,Fcouncil attempted to arrange an urgent
OL,18,Fvisit from both the pest and
OL,19,Felectrical teams to investigate this
OL,20,Fissue further.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
