OL,6,F"We are continuing to seek access to
OL,7,Fthe property to investigate and treat
OL,8,Fthis infestation.
OL,10,F"Our thoughts are with the individual
OL,11,Fand we will continue to work with the
OL,12,Ffamily to ensure her mother's home is
OL,13,Fsafe and free from pests."
OL,15,FJoan, who is recovering in hospital,
OL,16,Fwill go into respite care next week.
OL,18,FIt's unclear where she will live after
OL,19,Fthat but Andrea says her mum will
OL,20,Fnever return to the house again.
